data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail
data.value: Manan kayhinamanta hunt'achinkunanta kamachikunmanchu. Allinta qaway hinapuni willay kasqanta, utaq huk riqchaq hunt'achiy. Sichus kay willayta chaskikullankipuni, financiera llankana wasiwan tupanakuy.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail2
data.value: Huk pantay kasqa mayk'aq kay chaniyuq hunt'achina llankanakunapaq. Rantiqpa ruwayninman yanapakuypaq t'inkiy.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails. Probably, the PI is rejected by risk.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.BR
data.value: Kay tikrana mana uyakusqa atikunchu. Willayniykita chiqaqchay. Wakin hunt'achina tarjetakuna mana kay plataformapi chaskisqa atikunkuchu, chantapas ruwaspa huk hunt'achina tarhita nisqayku. Sichus pantayta qatin, wakiypa wasinniykita tinkiyta atikunki.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Brazil. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.MX
data.value: Kay tikrana mana uyakusqa atikunchu. Willayniykita chiqaqchay. Wakin hunt'achina tarjetakuna mana hunt'achina plataformapaq chaskisqa atikunkuchu imarayku harkaypa kamachinakuna kitipi kanan. Sichus pantayta qatin, wakiypa wasinniykita tinkiyta atikunki.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Mexico. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiLimitExceeded

data.name: Literal.Error.SaInIntermediateStatus

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.AR
data.value:
Quypaq qamta munasqa rurukunawan utaq yanapakuqkunawan huk ruwaqpa yupayninta paqarichinki. Sapa kuti musuq hunt'achina llankanakunata rurupaq utaq yanapakuypaq qunki kay qatiq willakuyta quyta atikuyku chaymanta ñawpaq qunki ari ñiy kanki. Proposito yupaypa paqarichiyniykipaq chaymanta/utaq musuq huntachina yacharichiyta yapachkan chayta munasqa kanku quypaq sapalla willayta kayhina: sutiyki, maypi kasqan, telefono yupay, correo electronicopa maypi kasqan, qullqi-mañaypa tarhita yupay chaymanta banco yupana yupay. IP maypi kasqan chaymanta dispositvoyki ID huñusqapas atikunki chaymanta huñusqa kay willakuyta sapanchasqa willaywan yupaypaq qunki utaq mayk'aq musuq hunt'achina llankanakunata yapachkanki.
Microsoft Corporation kaqman uyakuni, afiliadokunayuq chaymanta subsidiariokunayuq, ruwaypaq sapalla willayta chayta kaypi quyta tiyani, terminospi ruwasqanku Kamachi No. 25,326, kaqwan Ruwana 5 kaqpi propositokunapaq apachiypaq uyaychaykuna nuqaman chaymanta/utaq willariq imakuna rantikunapaq chaymanta/utaq yanapakuykunapaq tupachkanku. Ari ñini kay Kamachinawan No. 25,326, Ruwana 6 kaqpi, Willasqani kay voluntaria uynimanta kasqani.
Pantay qusqa willaymanta mana wakin consecuencia uyakunchu kay mana ruwasqa yaykunapaq rurukunamanta chaymanta yanapakuykunamanta kay web kitipi qusqan. Willayniy quni, uyniyman kasqani tiyaypaq kay waqaychasqa willayta willaqkunaq taqinpi Microsoft Corporation kaqmanta Redmond, WA 98052 kaqpi tarikusqan. Sapalla wilayniyuq derechosniyuq willay hina mana qullqiwan chaymanta intervalokunawan ruwayta kasqan chayta mana aswan suqta killakunakama huchuyachiyta kankuchu sichus mana evidencia allin munasqawan qusqa Kamachinapaq No. 25,326, Ruwana 14 kaqpi, Sullk'a ruwana 3 kaqpi ruwaypaq kasqan. Kamachiq kay Kamachi No. 25,326 kaqta kallpachkan kay ARGENTINE DIRECTORATE SAPALLA WILLAYMANTA HARKAYNINPAQ kanan chaymanta wakin willarikuywan chaymanta/utaq tapunawan qusqa sasachakuykunapaq kallpasqan ruwaypaq qusqa kamachina sapalla willaywan harkayninpaq.
Sapalla willayniyki yaykuyta utaq tikrayta atikunki kaypi: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Ruwanapi tikraypaq sapalla willayta akllanki kay qusqa uynita kaypi kanan chanta Microsoft Corporation uyakun huñuypaq chaymanta waqaychaypaq sapalla willayta hanaq hina willasqan.
Huk yupayta paqarichkan chaymanta Clicta ruwachkan “Uyakuy” ñitina uranpi chanta Microsoft Corporation sapalla willayniykiwan quyta ari ñinki chaymanta kaypi transferencia hina takyachisqan.
data.comment: Consent text for ES-AR

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.HU
data.value:
Rurukunata utaq qarakuykunata aswan ranqhanapaq ruraq yupanata paqarichina. Sapa huk musuq hunt'achina llankanakunata quspa rurukunapa utaq qarakuy kay willayta ari nisqaykita yachanapaq qatipanallapaqpuni. Rurachakuchtin chaymantapas yupanata paqarichinapaq utaq musuq hunt'achinapaq llankanakunata sapallaykipa willayniykita mañakunqa kanman: suti, tarichiy, telefono yupay, correo electronico maypi kasqan, qullqi-mañaypa tarhita yupay, chaymantapas banco yupanapa yupay. Chaymantapas IP tarichiyniykita uqharisunman chaymanta ID imantapas chaymanta kay willayta sapallanpa riqsichikuq willaywan tupanachiyta riqsisqata qusqaykiwan yupanata paqarichinapaq utaq musuq llankanakunata hunt'achiypa yapakuqtin.
Kay sapallaykipa riqsichikuq yupanapa willayniyki pallakuq kikillanpi musuq paqarichiy yupanaman apachikunqa iñisqamanhina kay Microsoft Corporation Estados Unidosmanta kuyuchiyniykitarurachinapaq chaymanta rurukunata qarakuykunata riqsichinapaq. Kay willaykuna kamachiq pacha nisqamanhina apaykachakunman. Microsoft Corporation manan sapallapa willayta apaykachanqachu kay hatun qillqapi qukusqata huk rikchaq ruwaykunapaq kay hatun qelqapi nikusqanmanhina, yapaspa hinapas manan marketing ruraykunata qunqaspa.
Microsoft hukman sapallaykipa willayniykita willanman. Willakuyniyki kuyuchiyniykipipuni rurayninpi mañakuqtin, kamachiq takiykunata ruraspa, mañasqaman kutichinapaq suwakuy manan kananpaq utaq kamachiypi kamachikunanpaq.
Manan sapallaykipa riqsichikuy willayniykita tikrankimanchu kaypi: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Sichus willayta tikrayta munanki kaypi churakuqta Microsoft Corporation munanki t'uqpinanta kunanpi sapallaykipa willayta apachinanpaq kuyuchinanpaq ñawpaq nikusqamanhina.
Musuq yupanata paqarichiy chaymanta clic ruway kay “Chaskikuy” wutunpi chaymanta Microsoft Corporation willayniykita t'uqpinanpaq ñuqanchakunki, sapallapa riqsichikuq willaywan chaymanta Microsoft pallayta kamachinanpaq, apachikuy chaymanta tupunakuy sapallap willay hukwan kay hatun qelqapa nisqanpaq.

data.name: Literal.PICVC.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Kaytahina hunt'achinaykita mañasuyku {0} {1} - {2} qullqi-mañaypa tarhitaykimanta.
  • Hunt'achisqaykita kutichupusaqku chiqaqhay takiyta rurakusqantawan.
  • Chiqaqchasqa kananpaq, mayk'apuni q'ipi kasqanta yaykuchiy UTAQ 3 ñup'unayuq cudigutakuyuchiypi imakunata quspa.
  • Mayk'aq hunt'achiyniykita tarinkiman utaq 3 ñup'unayuq cudiguta, qullqi-mañaypa tarhita qawapayaspa. Banco qarakuymanhina, kay telefonopi, utaq yupanaykipa imayna kayninta imprimispa rurakunamn chaskipi hamuqta.
  • Kay chiqaqyachita hunt'achinayki kanmi manaraq {3}, qamtaq {4} watiqmanta hinanayta atinkiman.
  • Sayayniykiman hina chaymanta banco sayayninman hina maypi tarjetata rurakusqanpi, Banco huk internacional hunt'achinata ninamn kuyuchiynaykimanta (ITF) utaq qullqi tikrakusqanmanta hina chiqaqchakuchqatin. Kay imakunata rurakunan atikusqanta chiqaqchanapaq, ima bancopi tarjetata urqhusqaykita tapuy. ITF hunt'achiyta utaq qullqi tikrayamta chiqaqchaspa rurakusqanta MANAN Microsoft kutichinqachu.
data.comment: PICVC term of use. {0} is for the currency. {1} is for the min amount to charge. {2} is for the max amount to charge. {3} is the exact time of challenge deadline. {4} is the left times to retry challenge.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.SubHeader
data.value: Kunan ñawpaq uyakusqa Microsoft hunt'achinakunapa chiqaqchayniyki ruwayta atikunki maypipaq PayPal hapirinalla kanan mayk'aq Microsoft kaqpi payllanki.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.US
data.value: PayPal kaqta qatiq hunt'achinakunapaq Microsoft plataformapi ruway. Sichus huk PayPal qullqi puchuq tiyanki, kay qullqi ñawpaq ruwasqan, sichus munasqa hunt'achina imaynata akllasqanki. Sichus mana huk munasqa hunt'achina imaynata akllasqankichu utaq ruwasqaña hunt'achinayki imaynapaq tukusqan utaq wischusqan, PayPal waqaychanayki hunt'achina imaynaykiman cargos qun. Hunt'achina imaynayki takyay utaq tikray atikunki, utaq kay uyakuyta wakin phanita Tupachiyniykipi Paypal.com kaqman tikray. Huk hunt'achina imaynata Tupachiyniykipi takyankikama, hunt'achina imaynata qatisqa hunt'achina kamachinakuna PayPal.com kaqpi ruwasqan.
data.comment: Text for United States, Canada, Brazil

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.DE
data.value: Ari ñinki kay Microsoft hunt'achina yacharichiykunanniyki PayPal kaqman mirachiyta atikun, chanta chiqa PayPal kaqwan Microsoft kaqpi Microsoft kaqman payllayta atikunki rikchisqa hunt'achina chaskiqkunapaq sichus kay Microsoft plataformata ruwachkanki. PayPal kaqta uyakunki qunakuypaq PayPal mirachiypa kaqninkunaykiwan Microsoft kaqwan kaq willakuy qunakusqa huk hunt'achina chaskiqniwan uran Sapalla Kamachinaykipi yapachkan. Kay Microsoft kaqta kawsarichin sichus hunt'achinayki allinlla tiyan chaymanta yanapaypaq llapa mirachiyniyki. PayPal Microsoft kaqta yachasun sichus ari ñinkiyki qichunki. PayPal kaqman ninki ruwaypaq hunt'achina mañakuykuna Microsoft kaqpaq apachisqan sichus qampaq hina uyakusqan. Sichus huk PayPal qullqi puchuq tiyanki, ñawpaq ruwasqa atikun. Sichus ruwasqañayki qallarisqa qallarinata wischusqan utaq tukusqan, waqaychasqayki qallarisqa qallarinapaq cargoswan kasqan. Kay uyakuynin chinkachiyta atikunki utaq munasqa qallarisqa qallarina wakin pachata PayPal yupayniykipi tikray. Sichus huk qullqi payllanki mana ñawpaq qullqipi PayPal Yupayniykipaq kanchu, PayPal qullqita tikran sichus kunan akllayta ruwachkanki.
data.comment: Text for Germany, Netherlands, Sweden, United Kingdom, Russia

data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Heading
data.value: An update to your PayPal account agreement with Microsoft
data.comment: PayPal Scenario Strings - Heading for the update Paypal billing agreement page

data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Subheading
data.value: By accepting this update, you'll be able to use your PayPal account wherever PayPal is available with Microsoft Pay.
data.comment: PayPal Scenario Strings - Subheading for the update Paypal billing agreement page

data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Text
data.value: You agree to allow Microsoft to transmit your PayPal payment instructions to PayPal for purchases directly to Microsoft or an identified payment recipient utilizing a Microsoft platform. If you have a PayPal balance, it will be used first. If your preferred or default funding source is declined or expired, your backup-funding source will be charged. You allow PayPal to share your PayPal transaction details with Microsoft. The sharing of PayPal transaction details enables Microsoft to know if your payment has been successful, to help fulfill your transaction and provide payment receipts as identified in PayPal's Privacy Policy. You instruct PayPal to treat payment requests sent by Microsoft as authorized by you per the PayPal User Agreement. If you pay in a currency that is not the primary currency of your PayPal Account, PayPal will convert the amount using our then current rate. You can cancel this authorization or change your preferred funding source at any time in your PayPal account. If you withdraw your consent to use PayPal on Microsoft, PayPal may inform Microsoft.
data.comment: PayPal Scenario Strings - Agreement text for the update Paypal billing agreement page
